%h1 Sensors
%hr
%i.fa.fa-info-circle
%strong Sensors a measuring devices connected to your reporter.box. Sensors are the main triggers for sensor live reports. These are all your sensors available. Add a new one!
%hr
%h3 Manage Sensors
%strong Do you have a new sensor? Register it here!
%p
=link_to new_sensor_path, {:class => "btn btn-primary btn-lg"} do
  %span.fa.fa-plus-circle
  Add new sensor

%hr
%h3 Listing Sensors
%strong This is a list of all registered sensors. Choose 
%i.fa.fa-eye &nbsp to view the sensor or 
%i.fa.fa-pencil-square-o &nbsp to edit it.
%table.table.table-striped.table-hover
  %tr
    %th Sensor-Name
    %th ID 
    %th Address
  - @sensors.each do |sensor|
    %tr
      %td
        =link_to sensor_path(sensor) do 
          =sensor.name   
          %i.fa.fa-eye
        =link_to edit_sensor_path(sensor) do
          %i.fa.fa-pencil-square-o 
      %td= sensor.id
      %td= sensor.address

